<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xiao-fan-qie-86-14" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xiao-fan-qie-86-14" class="zg-link" title="小番茄">小番茄</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$andrew-liou" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/andrew-liou" class="zg-link" title="Andrew Liou">Andrew Liou</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$kerenxxx" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/kerenxxx" class="zg-link" title="kerenxxx">kerenxxx</a></span>
